Ingredients:
3 gal apple juice
4.7 lbs extra light (pils) LME
3.3 lbs wheat LME

8 oz Special B
8 oz 60L crystal/caramel
4 oz torrified wheat
4 oz acidulated barley

Hops:
Northern brewer US
Cascade

Yeast:
English ale

Extras:
2oz Vanilla extract
4oz lactose


The boil:
All LME & apple juice to boil
T-60m: 1 oz Northern Brewer US
T-15m: 0.5 oz Cascade
     4 oz lactose
T-5m: 0.5 oz Cascade


Notes:
19.5% BRIX initial

Consider using salt in the future




